{"article_id":"HO6tlyozaGkJsWXB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford said Thursday","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"she ' s \" 100 percent \" certain","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett M. Kavanaugh is the person","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"who sexually assaulted her at a high school party ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"rejecting suggestions of mistaken identity or faulty memory 36 years later .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Her voice cracked with emotion during her opening statement to the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"when she described the social circuit in Montgomery County , Maryland ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"where she \" met Brett Kavanaugh , the boy","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"who sexually assaulted me . \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"While adding few details to the account","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"she told to reporters earlier this month ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"she did attempt to explain","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"why she came forward the way","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"she did , first anonymously and later publicly .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"She recalled specific details about the night of the assault ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"including Judge Kavanaugh and his friend , Mark Judge , \" drunkenly laughing during the attack. \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"After she escaped their clutches ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"she said ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"she heard them \" laughing and loudly walk down the narrow stairs ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"pin-balling off the walls on the way down . \"","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"But she apologized","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"for not remember when , where , or exactly who was at the party","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"where she says","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the assault took place .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"\" I don ' t have all the answers ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and I don ' t remember","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"as much","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"as I would like to , \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" But the details about that night","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that bring me here today","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"are ones","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"I will never forget .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"They have been seared into my memory","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and have haunted me episodically as an adult . \"","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Republicans tasked a sexual assault prosecutor , Rachel Mitchell , with asking questions ,","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"and she prodded Ms. Blasey Ford on her memory of the night .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"Democrats , meanwhile , tapped Ms. Blasey Ford ' s emotions","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"and dismissed gaps in her memory .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"\" A trauma survivor can not be expected to remember every painful detail , \"","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"said Sen. Richard Durbin , Illinois Democrat .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"He asked her","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"what the chance was","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"that it was Judge Kavanaugh and not someone else","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"who assaulted her .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"She said","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"she is \" 100 percent \" certain .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Under questioning from Sen. Dianne Feinstein , Ms. Blasey Ford said","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"she ' s faced years of anxiety and PTSD-like symptoms ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"and still suffers claustrophobia","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"- including demanding a second front door on her current home","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to have another escape route .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"She said","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"the chief impact came in the immediate years after the attack ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"when she struggled academically","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and had trouble making friends , particularly with boys .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"She told Ms. Feinstein","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"there was no question","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"it was Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" So , what you ' re telling us is this could not be a case of mistaken identity ? \"","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"the senator asked .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Her version of events has not been corroborated ,","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"and the three witnesses","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"she says","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"she remembers","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"were at the party","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"have each said","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"they can not recall anything like what she describes .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Since she came forward ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"she says","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"she has had to face death threats","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"and has been \" called the most vile and hateful names imaginable. \"","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"She now lives in \" various secure locales , \" under guard .","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"And she said","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"earlier this week her work email was hacked ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"and \" messages were sent out","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"supposedly recanting my description of the sexual assault . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":111,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":81,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":0,"right":80,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":1,"right":78,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":84,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":5,"right":83,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":6,"rig